<template>
    <v-card>
        <v-list-item two-line>
            <v-list-item-content>
                <v-list-item-title>Raporty</v-list-item-title>
                <v-list-item-subtitle>Generuj raporty w formie Excela </v-list-item-subtitle>
            </v-list-item-content>
        </v-list-item>

        <v-divider></v-divider>

            <v-card flat>
                <v-card-text>
                <v-container fluid>
                    <v-row>
                    <v-col
                        cols="12"
                        sm="4"
                        md="4"
                    >
                        <v-checkbox
                        v-model="ex4"
                        label="Raport Rev & GP"
                        color="red"
                        value="red"
                        hide-details
                        ></v-checkbox>
                        <v-checkbox
                        v-model="ex4"
                        label="Raport przesyłek"
                        color="red darken-3"
                        value="red darken-3"
                        hide-details
                        ></v-checkbox>
                    </v-col>
                    <v-col
                        cols="12"
                        sm="4"
                        md="4"
                    >
                        <v-checkbox
                        v-model="ex4"
                        label="Raport prowizji"
                        color="indigo"
                        value="indigo"
                        hide-details
                        ></v-checkbox>
                        <v-checkbox
                        v-model="ex4"
                        label="Zestawienie klientów"
                        color="indigo darken-3"
                        value="indigo darken-3"
                        hide-details
                        ></v-checkbox>
                    </v-col>

                    </v-row>

 
                </v-container>
                </v-card-text>
            </v-card>

    </v-card>
</template>

<script>


export default {
    data() {
        return {
        ex4: ['red', 'indigo', 'orange', 'primary', 'secondary', 'success', 'info', 'warning', 'error', 'red darken-3', 'indigo darken-3', 'orange darken-3'],
      }
    },

}
</script>

<style>

</style>
